General.Name: Pursuit Attractions and Hospitality, Inc.
General.Description: Pursuit Attractions and Hospitality, Inc., an attraction and hospitality company, owns and operates hospitality destinations in the United States, Canada, and Iceland. It operates various attractions and lodges with integrated restaurants, retail, and transportation facilities. The company was formerly known as Viad Corp and changed its name to Pursuit Attractions and Hospitality, Inc. in January 2025. Pursuit Attractions and Hospitality, Inc. was founded in 1926 and is based in Denver, Colorado.
